Create a logger for a module instance.

Parameters:
moduleName -
userAgent -
url - URL of top-level window, may be null for old browser plugins
tabKey - opaque key for the tab, may be empty string if the plugin can't distinguish tabs or null if using an old browser plugin
sessionKey - unique session key, may be null for old browser plugins
serverChannel - connection from the client
userAgentIcon - byte array containing an icon (which fits in 24x24) for this user agent or null if unavailable
Returns:
ModuleHandle instance -- caller is responsible for calling ModuleHandle.unload() on it when done
